6, \"to\": 2284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's the chest breaking the barrier that counts.Lyles' chest crossed first.\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2365, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the chest\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2304}, {\"ngram\": \"the barrier\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2325}, {\"ngram\": \"Lyles' chest\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2350}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was the closest 1-2 finish in the 100 since at least Moscow in 1980 - or maybe even ever.\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2425, \"end\": 2431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4827667229055787e-14, \"text\": \"Moscow\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the closest 1-2 finish\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2398}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Back then, Britain's Allan Wells narrowly beat Silvio Leonard in an era when the electronic timers did not go into the thousandths of a second.\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2606, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2474, \"end\": 2481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9933379061521227, \"rank\": 0.006706682693201891, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2484, \"end\": 2495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allan_Wells\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Allan Wells\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allan_Wells\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allan_Wells\"}, {\"begin\": 2510, \"end\": 2524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silvio_Leonard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Silvio Leonard\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/